{"tid":2505417,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓人感謝香港人: 《英雄本色》幫助南韓人度過「獨裁高壓時代」, 香港人最終也必能度過「獨裁高壓時代」.","createTime":"2021-04-26T14:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T14:46:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"407031fb56af9b23912f9292f72d7b2a656e09b0","tid":2505417,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jozev1969/posts/10158180648276009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjozev1969%2Fposts%2F10158180648276009&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6zHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=c10949c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jozev1969/posts/10158180648276009</a><br />\n<br />\n喬靖夫<br />\n7分鐘  &middot;<br />\n在《奔向未來日子》(英雄本色II主題曲)一個韓國樂團演奏版的YouTube底下，有位網友特意以英文向香港人留言。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，當年我們拍的《英雄本色》電影，曾經對韓國人民有很大的激勵作用，幫助他們度過軍事獨裁政權的高壓時代，因此韓國人至今一直對《英雄本色》具有深厚的感情。<br />\n最後他亦勉勵香港人，最終必能像韓國人一樣，成功改變命運。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmarPd7EDzFmGAEkgLUZwawh2VjA9HpU8Jk2A8otrC1mEe?filename=VYkOrdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYkOrdP.jpg&h=be0d5a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mJfgb7ySgeo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmJfgb7ySgeo&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6zHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=74d5e76e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mJfgb7ySgeo</a>"},{"pid":"d6e3bf338bf4c846cc9f1c7d175bccf039c80116","tid":2505417,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"電影既力量. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝南韓手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5fc3fd6b69f8dd9448fe7585530907ecdc4561","tid":2505417,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"演唱：張國榮(Leslie Cheung)<